    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s a total dream. This car is in truly pristine condition\u2014it still has that new-car feel and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered since day one, always kept in the garage, and is basically flawless inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and meticulously cared for, you\u2019ve found it. I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to be absolutely thrilled!",
