    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade FD3S RX-7, featuring the iconic 13B-REW sequential twin-turbocharged rotary powerplant. This specimen retains its factory-spec boost pattern with a flawless 10-8-10 transition. The chassis remains structurally pristine, showcasing original double-wishbone suspension components and a factory Torsen LSD for optimal power delivery. Zero evidence of thermal degradation in the engine bay; all vacuum lines have been meticulously maintained to OEM specifications. Compression test results are outstandingly uniform across all rotor faces, indicating a healthy apex seal life. Finished in its original paint with an interior that exhibits zero UV damage or bolster wear, this is a rare, unmolested example of 90s JDM engineering excellence.",
      "price": 46500.0,
